Package com.radiotelescope.repository.model.celestialBody

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CelestialBodySpecificationBuilder
    Builder used to build a class CelestialBodySpecification matching the list of class SearchCriteria entered by the user
    SearchCriteria
    Data class containing the enum Filter - the field - of a class CelestialBody entity. This is what field will be used to search
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Filter
    Enum class that acts as a search filter for the class CelestialBody entity
    SolarSystemBodies
    Due to the proximity of celestial bodies within our solar system, right ascension and declination must be calculated. This is different than other celestial bodies outside of our solar system, which are far enough away that the right ascension is declination is effectively static
